Roundcube Webmail RememberMe
============================
Rouncube plugin to add a remember_me checkbox in login.

When remember me is checked, it stores user, password and host encrypted in a cookie, and it will be used to login in a future time, even if you close the browser.

Install
=======
* Place this plugin folder into plugins directory of RoundCube
* Add remember_me to $rcmail_config['plugins'] in your RoundCube config

